ckquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前有個post 講中伏美食，今個post講吓唔中伏嘅美食啦！<br />\n<br />\n我推薦 美登利 ，壽司新鮮、抵食，又有中文menu , 一個字<br />\n平靚正黎形容！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sushinomidori.co.jp/shop.php?name=shibuya\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sushinomidori.co.jp%2Fshop.php%3Fname%3Dshibuya&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=944dbdf2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sushinomidori.co.jp/shop.php?name=shibuya</a><br />\n<br />\n有好幾間分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉谷分店勁多人 ，但套餐好抵食！<br />\n梅丘總店有限定日子放題！<br />\n池袋係迴轉壽司店！<br />\n<br />\n其實我只食過涉谷分店，排隊要排成1個鐘以上，但拎完飛可以周圍行吓先，好在附近都有好多野行！</blockquote><br />\n食放題留意梅丘係小村無野行咩<br />\n仲要去老練咁遠</blockquote><br />\n食放題真心浪費quota 仲要等咁耐。<br />\n留番個肚食其他野仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意！！食多兩餐好過，BTW 係日本倉燒肉都唔係太見日本食放題，佢地都係散嗌嘅多"},{"pid":"27c9c002aafed3a82e88b26c9c5924c80fd1969a","tid":242482,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d00ea783cb3b536054ab7e2357f3ea1ffe6f902e","tid":242482,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"冇中國人排隊嘅就多數係地道野"},{"pid":"8dc80906bed7c8a9a3af6167ea86eb007cd1e263","tid":242482,"uid":114124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"美登利世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有中文餐牌，但唔識日文唔太建議去食放題，因為唔似香港嗰啲放題咁有紙仔比你剔，而係直接同店員落order<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我上次去係坐吧枱，要直接向師傅order，係語言不通嘅情況下，師傅叫我地係中日對照嘅餐牌度抄啲壽司嘅日文比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d7be38f4efdb968795f06b1cb603c6afb38d50","tid":242482,"uid":60073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇中國人排隊嘅就多數係地道野</blockquote><br />\n地道唔代表好食，日本人人好簡單排隊只係得兩個原因一個係平，第二個係好平。當然都會有啲又平又好食但唔多（個人認為）"},{"pid":"1f9287f72127c2c7d6f8cf78412c94ae9e0b247e","tid":242482,"uid":52702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有間連鎖天丼專門店 我覺得好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  每月18號仲有個優惠 廿蚊到港紙有個特盛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講起都好想食 d天婦羅炸得好好味</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/111100_966be56269a83e804fceaa308612c732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F111100_966be56269a83e804fceaa308612c732.jpg&h=f190e31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪呢一間？呢間都 好正架！又勁多分店！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢間超正！ 天婦羅飯加埋冷烏冬/喬麥麵set 無得輸"},{"pid":"cb74f3d33fa6c9b02696f440b78b063c50829208","tid":242482,"uid":60073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"日本〒160-0022 Tōkyō-to, Shinjuku-ku, Shinjuku, 3 Chome&minus;３１ 新宿３丁目３１&minus;８ Tempura Tsunahachi Shinjuku Main Store<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog-imgs-41.fc2.com/t/o/k/tokiyadiary/P5230001_convert_20090524095950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog-imgs-41.fc2.com%2Ft%2Fo%2Fk%2Ftokiyadiary%2FP5230001_convert_20090524095950.jpg&h=71518e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tunahachi.co.jp/zh_tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tunahachi.co.jp%2Fzh_tw%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ac6cd619\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tunahachi.co.jp/zh_tw/</a><br />\n有無人食過呢間？"},{"pid":"7e5e1b751f9721cbf7e80bdaf284c390599ecb7c","tid":242482,"uid":39419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>井上拉麵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n井上拉麵 係築地企係到食嗰間？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"525450ed51c60fc06c6d94b52c6da4e7dfd19943","tid":242482,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike"